data.title: Starks Wins High Jump At Missouri Invitational
data.meta_description: COLUMBIA, MO. - Drake senior Katie Starks (Bellevue, Neb.) soared five feet 7 inches to capture the women's high jump Friday at the Missouri Invitational.Drake senior
data.text:
COLUMBIA, MO. - Drake senior Katie Starks (Bellevue, Neb.) soared five feet 7 inches to capture the women's high jump Friday at the Missouri Invitational.

Drake senior Kasey McDaniel (Spencer, Iowa) placed second in the women's 60 hurdles in 8.96 seconds. McDaniel was clocked in 8.83 seconds in the preliminaries.

Senior Jordan Malmstrm (Omaha, Neb.) was third in the men's 60-meter dash in 6.97 seconds. Junior Jaron VanMaanen (Sully, Iowa) was eighth in the men's high jump at 6-4 3/4.
